# Analysis of the Main Target Image

The main target image shows two separate structures:

## Structure 1 (Left Side - Tower-like Structure):
- Consists of 3 orange cylindrical blocks (index 9) stacked vertically
- A yellow horizontal bar (index 8) going across the middle cylinder
- A red house-like structure with an archway (index 1) on top of the yellow bar
- A yellow half-cylinder/dome (index 10) on top of the red house structure
- An orange triangular roof piece (index 14 or 15) at the very top

## Structure 2 (Right Side - Gate-like Structure):
- A yellow base bar (index 8) at the bottom
- Another yellow bar (index 8) at the top
- Six cube blocks arranged in two columns with three blocks each:
  - Left column (bottom to top): yellow (index 7), orange (index 5), green (index 4)
  - Right column (bottom to top): red (index 6), orange (index 5), blue (index 3)

Total blocks used: approximately 15 blocks across both structures.

# Selected Blocks from Dictionary

Based on my analysis, I need the following blocks from the dictionary:
- Red archway block (index 1)
- Blue cube (index 3)
- Green cube (index 4)
- Orange cube (index 5) - used twice
- Red cube (index 6)
- Yellow horizontal rectangular block (index 7)
- Yellow longer horizontal bar (index 8) - used three times
- Orange cylinder (index 9) - used three times
- Yellow half-dome/cylinder (index 10)
- Orange triangular roof piece (index 14 or 15, using 14)

# Assembly Order

```
{
    Step1: Move block with index 8
    Step2: Move block with index 7
    Step3: Move block with index 6
    Step4: Move block with index 5
    Step5: Move block with index 3
    Step6: Move block with index 4
    Step7: Move block with index 5
    Step8: Move block with index 8
    Step9: Move block with index 9
    Step10: Move block with index 9
    Step11: Move block with index 9
    Step12: Move block with index 8
    Step13: Move block with index 1
    Step14: Move block with index 10
    Step15: Move block with index 14
}
```

This assembly order builds the right structure first (steps 1-8), then proceeds to build the left tower structure (steps 9-15), working from the bottom up in each case.
